effective tax rate for each period reflects the benefit of these tax reductions in the consolidated return. ge makes cash payments to gecs for these tax reductions at the time ges tax payments are due. the effect of gecs on the amount of the
consolidated tax liability from the formation of the nbcu joint venture will be settled in cash when it otherwise would have reduced the liability of the group absent the tax on joint venture formation.
