retiree health and life benefits
we sponsor a number of retiree health and life insurance benefit plans (retiree benefit plans). principal retiree benefit plans are discussed below; other such
plans are not significant individually or in the aggregate. we use a december31 measurement date for our plans.  principal retiree benefit
plans provide health and life insurance benefits to certain employees who retire under the ge pension plan with 10 or more years of service. eligible retirees share in the cost of healthcare benefits. these plans cover approximately 216,000
retirees and dependents.
